 EDITOR'S NOTE: <PERSON> Laurinda </PERSON> <PERSON> Keys </PERSON>, an AP correspondent based in <LOCATION> Johannesburg </LOCATION>, has covered southern <LOCATION> Africa </LOCATION> since 1986.
