<TEXT>
 Energy futures prices changed little in one of the quietest weeks the market has seen in months. Supply-and-demand news was scarce, with continuing labor problems in the <LOCATION> North </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Sea </LOCATION> providing most of the action.
